Lab Comments: The back side of this tablet bears the imprint 93/150.  It is a generic pharmaceutical tablet containing 30 mg Codeine Phosphate and 300 mg Acetaminophen.  A generic version of Tylenol 3.
Warning: Please note that when this pill is turned upside down, the '3' could be read as an 'E'.  It was submitted to ecstasydata under the name 'E', suggesting this might be a common confusion when this pill is sold in the ecstasy market.  Pills with the numbers and markings like this one on the back are always pharmaceutical tablets.
